    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The Prime Minister confirms that, and, that being so, I do not see how he can reconcile that with the somewhat derisory attitude which the Minister of Fuel and Power adopted towards this matter.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
